tool_description:
Travlinq collaborates with the world's leading hotels, airlines, and car service providers to offer end-to-end booking services for Hotels, Flights, and Cars. The modular design of our API means you can easily customize the traveler booking Journey to suit your business’ needs. And with the continuous innovation of API you will get world latest traveling business features as well.

For more details visit :  https://apidocs.travlinq.net/
